入嚟屌你嫁"},{"pid":"2d463d1c6c5c813022f64861bdef14eb93f2cd92","tid":2195280,"uid":124690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"粗略分析intel 同 Amd有咩優劣<br />\n<br />\nIntel 奉行1個die 原則，製造難度係極高<br />\n相比起Amd 成本上都高好多<br />\n<br />\nIntel 製程雖然一直卡關，但14nm可以用到今日證明intel其實的確有料到 （但台電5nm都出埋）<br />\n<br />\nIntel 單核優勢的確冇人質疑到，論多核amd 當之無愧。單核intel 頻率最高，全核頻率喺10核以上啲產品上，Amd係比intel高<br />\n<br />\n綜合所有野，amd 成本低過intel<br />\n<br />\nIntel打機/用adobe野會好過amd (食單核）<br />\n<br />\nIntel用電會高過amd"},{"pid":"ac428374f2d19f49595c9644260d4559574a0057","tid":2195280,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"AMD yes. 但係成屋intel"},{"pid":"ca03980f39d7b90db6d21b748fc742c8e410902c","tid":2195280,"uid":46333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"Z490 + 10900k boom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0ed0d5e5aa341ce56216e2f32906e93297511a","tid":2195280,"uid":334722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"本身想出3900XT<br />\n諗諗下都係10900K<br />\n不過z490諗緊用tomahawk定unify好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a9e5c45d23d852fc4db7951984d24f848a486c","tid":2195280,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />intel"},{"pid":"94a7b9eea15596568056a1ce5fb6b6994c99b9f7","tid":2195280,"uid":236627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"股票買amd，但老婆用煙條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c060e484f0841d35d7ec39cb8e88797e7b00025a","tid":2195280,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f24801b80858d440b630df5020c679d34c24f1","tid":2195280,"uid":240069,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4578a0c579799a208766544334b20445a2b40742"